al/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 樓面 - 比啲客撚完比廚房佬撚<br />\n<br />\n廚房 - 係比廚房大佬撚姐<br />\n<br />\n做過三年廚房"},{"pid":"282ed4510aa4fe3f184e18b763d2154ec563139f","tid":238141,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓面 - 比D客撚<br />\n<br />\n廚房 - 比樓面撚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 樓面 - 比啲客撚完比廚房佬撚<br />\n<br />\n廚房 - 係比廚房大佬撚姐<br />\n<br />\n做過三年廚房</blockquote><br />\n可能你果間樓面同廚房無完全交流<br />\n溝通都交比廚房大佬（同監菜）"},{"pid":"90b229df2c5f721fbd427b25bd33cf4aad5d89c0","tid":238141,"uid":42097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓面 - 比D客撚<br />\n<br />\n廚房 - 比樓面撚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 樓面 - 比啲客撚完比廚房佬撚<br />\n<br />\n廚房 - 係比廚房大佬撚姐<br />\n<br />\n做過三年廚房</blockquote><br />\n可能你果間樓面同廚房無完全交流<br />\n溝通都交比廚房大佬（同監菜）</blockquote><br />\n我地間野用電腦入機<br />\n廚房入面有個mon響自己崗位<br />\n基本上係直接同樓面溝通<br />\n比班垃圾樓面玩撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣錯單，一陣個客又有D騎尼要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258d53adc097d398d1d24bc02b3514c5ff20bb98","tid":238141,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 餐廳廚房佬話事喎</blockquote><br />\n啱啊"},{"pid":"f38977ede8d35878451638dbd7473335ae17fd86","tid":238141,"uid":65893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-