T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓面慘好撚多<br />\n啲客吹單又唔知去唔去吹廚房好<br />\n又要比客屌 做到隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n催單我基本上唔會理，廚房係咁快就咁快，除咗只會檢查有冇漏單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知 但循例都要扮吹<br />\n叫蒸魚個啲客閪冧咁吹都唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c766ae13332e386f7be788cd7d455b7d632ff4","tid":238141,"uid":90791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:51:12.000Z","msg":"做廚房最後要留低收尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓面最多都係掃下地<br />\n廚房1星期最少洗3次地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做日本野仲要抹埋雪格 清冰 又凍又臭又多血水"},{"pid":"eed47de42d1020793d68b51db058f4300722bef8","tid":238141,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做廚房最後要留低收尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓面最多都係掃下地<br />\n廚房1星期最少洗3次地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做日本野仲要抹埋雪格 清冰 又凍又臭又多血水</blockquote><br />\n我做樓面一樣要洗雪櫃，康要洗廁所"},{"pid":"871e9a155c1c90dd36ccada999b0b56b33708f40","tid":238141,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"樓面撚鳩到廚房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓面先最受氣<br />\n廚房大佬玩野成間餐廳唔洗開門"},{"pid":"49d9b74cda80f87ec98dfec4f3deb1b0741524aa","tid":238141,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做廚房最後要留低收尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓面最多都係掃下地<br />\n廚房1星期最少洗3次地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做日本野仲要抹埋雪格 清冰 又凍又臭又多血水</blockquote><br />\n掃下地?<br />\n仲要洗埋拖埋地抹埋枱擺傢俬<br />\n攰到死仲要夜晚炒場繼續做<br />\n做樓面先慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde701c3d1b6a027cf4297819bf67074561ce2db","tid":2